LEE v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 12,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided November 13, 1964.

Before Henderson, C. J., and Hammond, Prescott, HornEy, Sybert and Oppenheimer, J].

*634Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Hamill in the court below.

Application denied..
